# 3. 個展って何？

Mizuki: What? You're helping with a solo exhibit?
Ena: Yeah, as part of a special lesson for my art class.
Ena: To be fair, it's gonna be just me and Mr. Yukihira.
Mafuyu: I see.
Rin: Wait, what's a solo exhibit?
Len: Uhh... Is it different from the ones they do at art museums?
Ena: So, your standard art exhibit usually involves displaying various works revolving around a certain theme...
Ena: But a solo exhibit involves the works of just one artist.
Ena: Like this...
Len: So many paintings... This is amazing.
Rin: There's stuff other than paintings too.
Ena: Yeah, some solo exhibits focus on sculptures or other inanimate objects. It all depends on what the artist wants to express.
Len: I see...
Mizuki: It's pretty cool how you can get a glimpse of what's going on inside the artist's head based on what they put on display!
Miku: So, what are your tasks going to involve?
Ena: Hmm, could be a number of things... But since they've already picked out a venue and what to put on display, I'll probably be helping move the paintings and putting up decorations.
Kanade: That sounds like a lot of physical work...
Len: But sounds fun...
Mafuyu: Are you interested, Len?
Len: Y-Yeah... I really wanna see what it looks like once all the paintings are put up.
Rin: Me too.
Rin: So, Ena, can we come see it...?
Ena: What?
Ena: Umm... I mean, sure...
Mizuki: Is something wrong?
Ena: Nothing's wrong per se...
Ena: But this is his... My dad's exhibit...
Mizuki: What...?
Mizuki: Are you sure you're gonna be okay?
Ena: I think so, but I'm not really looking forward to it...
Len: ...? Is it bad that you're helping your dad with his exhibit...?
Ena: Bad isn't quite it... It's just that, we have some history between us...
Len: H-History...?
Len: Umm...
Ena: Don't worry about me. I'll probably be fine.
Ena: Again, I'm not looking forward to it...
Ena: But there must be a reason why my teacher offered to give me a special lesson, so I don't wanna pass up this opportunity.
Mizuki: Ena...
Mizuki: Okay.
Kanade: Good luck.
Ena: *Nod* Thanks.
Ena: I'll probably be helping set everything up in the morning. Rin, Len, you two can come over whenever during that time.
Len: O-Okay...
